INSERT INTO posts (did, rkey, blob_cid, blob_mime_type, title, blob_alt_text, tags, languages, created_at, ingested_at)
         VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8, $9, extract(epoch from now())::BIGINT) ON CONFLICT(did, rkey) DO UPDATE SET title = excluded.title, blob_alt_text = excluded.blob_alt_text, tags = excluded.tags, edited_at = extract(epoch from now())::BIGINT
